## Requirements:
NodeJS/NPM: https://nodejs.org/dist/v10.15.3/node-v10.15.3-x64.msi
Postman: https://dl.pstmn.io/download/latest/win64

## Installation Steps (on CMD on linux):
> mkdir TOTP-APP && cd TOTP-APP
> npm init -y
> npm install express body-parser speakeasy --save


## Code
Paste the app.js file in the TOTP-APP folder.

## Running
> node app.js
> listening on :3000


## Output
The server has started on localhost:3000.
We can use Postman to check the responses.